value: Breeds on the west and east coasts of the North Atlantic from Sable Island to Long Island, in Florida, Bermuda, the Bahamas, British Hon- duras, the Lesser Antilles and Aruba Island; in the British Isles, islands off Jutland, coast of Brittany and coast of Tunisia; perhaps formerly on Madeira and the Azores. Winters from Louisiana and the Bahamas to Brazil, and to Madeira, the Azores and South Africa.^
